for 'Truth&quot; . . .</span><hr size=1> Hey guys, I know about zero japanese and I wanted to put a tattoo of the Kanji symbol for 'truth' on my character's chest. Can someone plz lmk what it looks like. I have a Japanese font btw, so u can type it or draw it. Thanks in advance! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ucryptinitedemon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cryptinite Demon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/28/02 12:47:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=874.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .</span><hr size=1> Well, I don't want to be responsible for you getting a wrong tattoo.  There are a few forms here I can give you<br>
<br>
死ね実 this means true fact<br>
真実性 this means the quality of being true<br>
誠実さ sincerity<br>
心理   principle, concept<br>
<br>
Now some parts of some of those are kana japanese characters, so some might not be full kanji cause of the suffixes/prefixes.  You might want to get these checked by Aoh-jp or maimaipanda first.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/umaimaipanda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>maimaipanda</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/28/02 1:57:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=874.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.sit.wisc.edu/~mamiller2/images/playing2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> as cryptinite said, there are several different words depending on what nuance of 'truth' you want.  I would think that &quot;shinjitsu&quot;:<br>
<br>
真実<br>
<br>
would be a good, all around choice.  <p><center><B> <I>Mamonaku. 11ban sen ni  Panda densha ga mairimasu.  <BR>Abunai desu kara, kiiro no sen no uchigawa made osagarikudasai.  </I> </B></center>
